(10718, 4935, 'post_content', 'Event Description Following this years successful event, The Big London Night Walk will return on Thursday2nd March 2017. Register your interestfor a Friday night with a difference, and change the lives of hardworking Big Issue vendors on their journeys away from homelessness. Event content The auction will be started in the morning of Thursday, April 13, 2017 at Center Hotel. There are over 100 featuredpictures that will be auctioned in this charity event. Expected the starting price of photograph is 20,000$. The winner isthe bidder offering the highest price. Other bidders also can contribute our fund by our charity box. All money earned in this charity event will donate to people that our volunteer photographers went to. Anyphilanthropist, nonprofit organization, NGO want to donate or ask any question, let contact with our staff. Who come with us? Kenny Martinez Support Staff Steven Walker CEO Alex Roberts Support Staff Tony Support Staff Jack David Support Staff Kevin Harris Support Staff'),
